      <title>Setting up your new Mac for academic work</title>
      <link>/post/new_install/</link>
      <pubDate>Wed, 07 Jun 2017 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate>
      
      <guid>/post/new_install/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;This is mainly for my own use, but I figured it might be useful to put it on-line&amp;hellip;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

